description:
This is a 17 minute workout called '15 MIN STRETCH FOR SPLITS (front splits flexibility routine)' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Do this 15 min stretch routine #WithMe to get your FRONT SPLITS! This is a great BEGINNERS guide to getting your splits. We are focusing on hamstring and hip flexibility in this one. This is a great routine to include into your daily life if getting your splits is your goal!
